  <owl:Ontology rdf:about="https://compass.local/ontology/intelligence#">
    <rdfs:label>COMPASS feature ontology: INTELLIGENCE</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment>AOMIC ID1000: 928 healthy Dutch young adults. The features grouped here are self-report / questionnaire measures: NEO-FFI Big Five personality, BIS/BAS reinforcement sensitivity, STAI trait anxiety, demographics, anthropometrics, socio-economic status, sexual/gender identity ratings and religiosity. Group measures from the same instrument or construct together. (Brain imaging features - FreeSurfer morphometry and the functional connectome - are placed deterministically under a single BRAIN domain via explicit paths and are not part of this semantic grouping step.)</rdfs:comment>
  </owl:Ontology>
